text: Phrissoma crispum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Johan Christian Fabricius in 1776. It is known from South Africa.BioLib.cz - Phrissoma crispum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1776
title: Phrissoma crispum
